nts for those who prefer this structure our ethical strategies are currently only available as segregated portfolios   total return strategies read more income strategies read more about income ethical strategies read more about ethical the value of investments and any income from them can fall and you may get back less than you invested by accepting this cookie you agree to heartwood storing your information this will not be passed on to any third parties and will need to be re accepted in  months to find out more please visit our cookie policy page  accept decline